title: 641. Championship Sunday Preview + Breaking Down Top College QBs
itunes:title: 641. Championship Sunday Preview + Breaking Down Top College QBs
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys react to the news of the Detroit Lions hiring Dan Campbell to be their new head coach and further discuss what the team can do in the offseason (3:00). Next, the pair analyze the traits of the top college quarterback prospects (8:15). To wrap up the show, the duo preview the Championship Sunday games of the Tampa Bay Buccaneers at the Green Bay Packers and the Buffalo Bills at the Kansas City Chiefs (30:32). Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
